author: sctemme
msg: The ActiveMQ checkout tried to check out the root of its repository, which
lands it a 400 Bad Request courtesy of mod_dontdothat.  Use the ASF Subversion
repository descriptor instead, and check out trunk.  Do away with the
special ActiveMQ repository descriptor since it doesn't seem to be used
anywhere else.  Hope I'm not breaking stuff.
